OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FModern slavery rockets in  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffive years to 50 million   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Modern slavery is a growing challenge  
OL,6, thanks to a mix of armed conflict,     
OL,7, climate change and the global pandemic,
OL,8, a new UN report says.                  
OL,10,FInternational Labour Organisation (ILO)
OL,11,Festimates suggest that 50 million      
OL,12,Fpeople - or one out of every 150 people
OL,13,Falive - are trapped in forced labour or
OL,14,Fforced marriages.                      
OL,16,FThat is up nearly 10 million on its    
OL,17,Fnumbers from five years ago.           
OL,19,FThe ILO said the fact things were      
OL,20,Fgetting worse was "shocking".          
